<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Activity</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styleHF.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styleForm.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styleActivities.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styleHF_ALL.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styleActivity1.css">

</head>
<body>

    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/ee4053c9b9.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <%- include("partials/headerPages.ejs") %>

    <div class="body">
    <div class="group">
        <h1 id="h">
          <% if(activity1!=="") { %>
          <h1><%= activity1[0].Header %></h1>
        <% }; %> 
      </h1>
        <span> <% if(activity1!=="") { %>
          <%=activity1[0].Days %>
          <% }; %> 
        </span> &nbsp;
        <span class ="rating">
          <% if(activity1 !== "") {%>
          <% if(activity1[0].Rate === "0") { %>
            <i class="fa-regular fa-star"></i>
            <i class="fa-regular fa-star"></i>
            <i class="fa-regular fa-star"></i>
            <i class="fa-regular fa-star"></i>
            <i class="fa-regular fa-star"></i>
            <% } %>
        <% if(activity1[0].Rate==="1") { %>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
            <% } %>
            <%  if(activity1[0].Rate==="2") { %>
             <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
             <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
             <% } %>
             <% if(activity1[0].Rate==="3") { %>
             <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
             <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
             <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
             <% } %>
             <% if(activity1[0].Rate==="4") { %>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
             <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
             <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
             <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
             <% } %>
             <% if(activity1[0].Rate==="5"){ %>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              <% } %>
          <% } %>
        </span>
        &nbsp;
        <span>
          <% if(activity1!=="") {%>
            <%=activity1[0].Rate %>
          <% } %>
        </span>
        &nbsp;
    </div>
    <br>
<div class="grid">
    <div class="mySlides">
        <div class="numbertext">1 / 3</div>
          <img src="/images/activities/<%=activity1[0].Picture[0]%>" style="width:100%">
      </div>
    
      <div class="mySlides">
        <div class="numbertext">2 / 3</div>
          <img src="/images/activities/<%=activity1[0].Picture[1]%>" style="width:100%">
      </div>
    
      <div class="mySlides">
        <div class="numbertext">3 / 3</div>
          <img src="/images/activities/<%=activity1[0].Picture[2]%>" style="width:100%">
      </div>
      
      <a class="prev" onclick="plusSlides(-1)">&#10094;</a>
      <a class="next" onclick="plusSlides(1)">&#10095;</a>
</div>
      
    <br>
    <div>
        <div class="text" >
          <% if(activity1!=="") {%>
            <h1><%=activity1[0].BriefDes %></h1>
          <% }; %> 
        </div>
    </div>
    <div>
        <h2><ins>DETAILS:</ins></h2>
        <h4>Full Description: </h4>
        <div class="w">
            <div>
              <% if(activity1!=="") {%>
                <h1><%=activity1[0].DetailedDes %></h1>
              <% }; %> 
             </div>
        </div>
        <h4>Plan: </h4>
        <div class="w">
                <div>
                  <% if(activity1!=="") {%>
                    <h1><%=activity1[0].Plan %></h1>
                  <% }; %> 
                </div>
        </div>
        <h4>About the Trip: </h4>
        <div class="w">
            <span><i class="fa-sharp fa-solid fa-xmark"></i></span>&nbsp
            <span class="more">
              <% if(activity1!=="") {%>
                <h1><%=activity1[0].CancelDet %></h1>
              <% }; %> 
              </span>
        </div>
        <div class="w">
            <span><i class="fa-regular fa-clock"></i></span>&nbsp
            <span class="more">
              <% if(activity1!=="") {%>
                <h1><%=activity1[0].Duration %></h1>
              <% }; %>
              </span>
        </div>
        <div class="w">
            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-bus"></i></span>&nbsp
            <span class="more"> 
              <% if(activity1!=="") {%>
                <h1><%=activity1[0].PickupDet %></h1>
              <% }; %>
              </span>
            </div>

    </div>

  

    <h2><ins>Select participants and date</ins></h2>
    <div class="book" id="book">
      <div>
        <input id="dropbtn" list="Adults" placeholder="Select number: ">
        <datalist id="Adults">
          <option value="1"></option>
          <option value="2"></option>
          <option value="3"></option>
          <option value="4"></option>
          <option value="5"></option>
          <option value="6"></option>
          <option value="7"></option>
          <option value="8"></option>
          <option value="9"></option>
          <option value="10"></option>
        </datalist>
        <div id="msg" class="check-error"></div>
      </div>
        <div>
          <!--<input id="dat" type="date" placeholder="Date" >
          <div id="date-msg" class="check-error"></div>-->

          <input id="dropbtn1" list="days" placeholder="Days Available">
          <datalist id="days">
            <option value=<%=activity1[0].AvailableDate %>></option>
          </datalist>
          <div id="date-msg" class="check-error"></div>
        </div>
        <div> 
          <button id="check" onclick="view()">Check Availability</button>
        </div>
       
        <script src="js/Activity1.js"></script>
      </div>

      <div id="avail">
        <h2><ins>Available</ins></h2>
        <div class="duration">
        <span><i class="fa-regular fa-clock"></i></span>&nbsp
        <span><%=activity1[0].Duration %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="cancel">
        <span><i class="fa-sharp fa-solid fa-xmark"></i></span>&nbsp
        <span><%=activity1[0].CancelDet%></span>
        <span id="time"> </span>
        </div>
        <div class ="price">
          <span>Total Price: </span>
          <span id="num1"> </span>
          <span>*</span>
          <span id="price1"><%=activity1[0].Price%></span>
          <span>=</span>
          <span id="total1"> </span>
      </div>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
          <button>Add To Cart</button>
        </div>

      </div>
      <script src="js/Activity1.js"></script>


      <h2><ins>Reviews</ins></h2>
      
      <div class="first">
                      
        <div class="reviews">
                <div class="rev">
                    <h6 class="R">Jan Erik L wrote a review Jan 2023</h6>
                </div>
                <div class="rating">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                </div>
                    <p class="R">"Thank you very much for your positive review of your recent holiday with us at Jaz Makadina.
                   We are happy to read about your experience with our hotel facilities and services.
                   We appreciate you taking the time to share your experience on Tripadvisor and we are 
                   looking forward welcoming you back at our hotel in the future."</p>
        </div>


        <div class="reviews">
            <div class="rev">
                <h6 class="R">Tony Nagy L wrote a review Feb 2023</h6>
            </div>
            <div class="rating">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fa-solid fa-star-half-stroke"></i>
            </div>
                <p class="R">"I've stayed at the Four Season Cairo Nile Plaza twice prior to booking this trip for my family. As it 
                    was their first time to Cairo wanted to make it special so we booked the Four Seasons again. Weeks leading up to 
                    the trip, the Concierge was incredibly helpful in assisting us with planning the best itinerary to make the most 
                    of our trip."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reviews">
          <div class="rev">
              <h6 class="R">Sara Samy L wrote a review Dec 2022</h6>
          </div>
          <div class="rating">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
          </div>
              <p class="R">"It’s a bit outside of downtown, but given that we weren’t looking to do any self exploring 
                  of the city this was not an issue. The hotel property is safe and very pleasant, built around a lovely pool 
                  area on the banks of the Nile with great views of the Valley of Kings when lit at night. Would 
                  definitely stay here again if I returned to Luxor."</p>
      </div>


    </div>
    </div>

    <script src="js/jazhotel.js"></script>

    <%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>

</body>
</html>